  <title>Admonishments</title>

  <subtitle>An docbook2odf example</subtitle>

  <info>
    <date>2013-12-07</date>

	<author>
      <personname>
		<firstname>Dylan</firstname>
		<surname>Moonfire</surname>
      </personname>
	</author>

    <abstract>
      <para>Admonishments are notes in the text, such as info, tips,or warnings.</para>
    </abstract>
  </info>

  <para>This article shows various examples of admonishments.</para>

  <note>
	<para>This is a note.</para>

	<para>This is the second line.</para>
  </note>
  <important>
	<para>This is a important.</para>

	<para>This is the second line.</para>
  </important>
  <warning>
	<para>This is a warning.</para>

	<para>This is the second line.</para>
  </warning>
  <caution>
	<para>This is a caution.</para>

	<para>This is the second line.</para>
  </caution>
  <tip>
	<para>This is a tip.</para>

	<para>This is the second line.</para>
  </tip>

</article>
